        <view class="feat-item"><text class="dot">•</text>真人发音 & 单词本收藏</view>
        <view class="feat-item"><text class="dot">•</text>长辈关怀模式（超大字体/夜间模式）</view>
        <view class="feat-item"><text class="dot">•</text>语音串读、导出文档打印</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="divider"></view>

    <view class="sub-section">
      <view class="sub-title badge-blue">📅 未来规划</view>
      <view class="feature-list">
